.Dd April 24, 2008
.Dt RC-sstat 8 SMM
.Os OpenRC
.Sh NAME
.Nm rc-sstat
.Nd show status info about services supervised by s6 then rc-status
info
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
gathers and displays information about the status of services supervised
by s6 then runs rc-status to show info about normal OpenRC services.
.Pp
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Nm
exits 1 if there is an internal error or exits with the same exit codes
as rc-status.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr rc-status 8 ,
.Xr rc-update 8
